From: YouTube Premium no-reply@youtube.com To: jakson1234@gmail.com Subject: Welcome to YouTube Premium Welcome to YouTube Premium Enjoy YouTube and YouTube Music ad-free Check out all of your member benefits: • Ad-free and background play Watch videos without ads, and keep them playing while using other apps. • Downloads Save videos to play offline, when traveling, or when you want to save on data. • Member perks From exclusive artist events to special product offers, you’ll also get extra YouTube benefits coming your way. • YouTube Music Premium Listen to over 100 million songs, get personalized mixes, discover the latest hits, and more with our music app — all without ads. • Watch YouTube Kids uninterrupted Have kids? Premium benefits also extend to YouTube Kids, an app made just for kids. This means both you and your child can watch all the videos you love ad-free, offline, and in the background. Download YouTube Kids from Google Play or the App Store. Don’t forget to get the YouTube Music app. It’s included in your membership.

From: YouTube no-reply@youtube.com To: rajeshtiwari.bro@gmail.com Subject: Won’t you miss all this? Won’t you miss all this? Renew your membership to keep these benefits. RENEW NOW If you don’t renew you’ll lose access to these member benefits: • Ad-free and offline. You won’t be able to enjoy YouTube ad-free, offline, and in the background. • YouTube Music Premium. You'll hear ads in the YouTube Music app and won't be able to play songs with your screen locked.

You may cancel your Music Premium membership anytime from your Apple ID account settings.

From: YouTube Premium Team no-reply@youtube.com To: hello@smilesdavis.yeah Subject: Updates to Your YouTube Premium Lite Plan Thank you for being a Premium Lite member. We hope you'll continue to be a member, but you can cancel your membership at any time. To check your account status and billing information, go to your Settings > Purchases & Memberships page. For more information about Premium Lite, visit our YouTube Help Center. We value your feedback and are always learning. Sincerely, The YouTube Premium Team

From: YouTube Premium no-reply@youtube.com To: michelkhanwald@gmail.com Subject: Your YouTube Premium price is increasing Hi Michel, We created YouTube Premium to provide an uninterrupted YouTube experience, so you can get closer to the videos, creators, and music artists that you love. To continue delivering great service and features, we will be increasing your Premium price from ARS 119.00/month to ARS 389.00/month. This change will take place on your next billing cycle starting on or after November 21, 2022. To check the status of your account and billing information, go to your Settings > Purchases and Memberships page. All members have the flexibility to pause or cancel anytime here. YouTube Premium will keep delivering the benefits you enjoy, like ad-free YouTube with background and offline play, and uninterrupted access to over 100 million songs with the YouTube Music app. Members also get to try experimental new features and exclusive livestream afterparties with music artists. This update will allow us to develop even more Premium features and continue to support the creators and artists you watch on YouTube. You can find more information on the latest updates in the YouTube Help Center.
